s: Test message\".\nActually, the simplest is best. Just the text.\n\nWait, looking at the prompt instructions again. I am an AI assistant.\nOkay, let's keep it simple.\n\n\"Test message\"\n\nOr should I include the instruction? No, repeat the *message*.\nOkay, \"Test message\".\n\nLet's double-check the history provided in the `user` block.\nThe first user message is \"Test message\".\nThe second user message is \"Repeat my previous message\".\nSo the target text is indeed \"Test message\".\n\nI will respond with that text.cw"
